{
  "stem": "1965.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 70.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I regret anything, it's not having been sensitive enough in my teenage years to take down notes on paper about certain names and cert-- I remember things that my mother and father talked about.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But certain names and things like that should be written down on paper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I never-- until today, and I asked my brothers-- the name of that labor camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do not know the name of the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, it was a labor camp where you went to work for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if you were weak and so forth, they, they knew to exterminate you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not precisely there, but they knew to take you away for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In one word, Jews were used for two purposes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One, to elimination, because to them, you had no value.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other one, to keep you working until they knew what to do with you, because they needed certain work loads done.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Also, the experimentations, which everybody has documented already, regarding the use of human skin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The experimentation of women's fertilities, all these things that were used from the human body to experiment in the name of experimentation, that truly to torture.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was really behind it all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when people keep saying it never happened-- is beyond my comprehension, why people cannot accept the truth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Do they need far more to go than to see that in 1994 a half a million people were slaughtered in a few weeks time in Rwanda, Africa.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There has been exterminations on this Earth when there is a genocide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Genocides happen on and off on this Earth amongst us humans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've been trying to find the answers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why is genocide happening amongst human beings?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it is not just because of religion, or because of money.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
